"v.解释；翻译 【英】 v. 解释 (to explain or interpret)；翻译 (to translate orally) 【记】 con＋strue=struct( 结构)→弄清结构→解释 【例】 You can construe what he said in a number of different ways. v. 解释 = explain = interpret; 口译翻译 【记】con, strue = struct结构－弄清结构－解释cons读: 看似; true真实的: 看似真实的, 但又不一定是真实的, 那么就需要解释一下. 比如你要作假的成绩单, 美国老一看, 有点儿怀疑, 就会让你解释一下成绩的由来. (不要作假! ) 【记】con + 音：释出，解释出真意；音：看 + true，看是不是true 需要分析，解释，翻译 construe (v.)  late 14c., from Late Latin construere ""to relate grammatically,"" in classical Latin ""to build up, pile together"" (see construction); also see construct (v.), which is a later acquisition of the same word. Related: Construed; construing; construal."
